}

### 12. Listar Imóveis (com filtros)
GET {{baseUrl}}/properties?pageNumber=1&pageSize=20&minPrice=100000&maxPrice=500000&municipality=Lisboa
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 13. Obter Imóvel por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/properties/{property-id}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 14. Pesquisar Imóveis
GET {{baseUrl}}/properties?searchTerm=Lisboa&type=1&status=0&minBedrooms=2
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 15. Imóveis em Destaque
GET {{baseUrl}}/properties?featuredOnly=true&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

